txt.en: 'Several Corsair captains have been spotted within the large cave beneath Emyn Ernil. I suppose without a ship they cannot be regarded as captains anymore, since they are directing the digging and mining efforts. Let's call them foremen instead.\n\n'Head into the cave and eliminate them. Without leadership the miners will cease digging and we can slow down their operation.'
Corsair foremen are directing the digging within the large cave under Emyn Ernil.
'Without direction their mining efforts will slow for the foreseeable future.'
Emyn Ernil Cave - Captain Without a Ship
The Corsair foremen are patrolling the large cave beneath Emyn Ernil.\n\nLhossil asked you to defeat the Corsair foremen directing the miners beneath Emyn Ernil.
Lhossil can be found in Dol Amroth.\n\nLhossil will be very pleased to hear the Corsair foremen have been eliminated.
